  "text": "So far, we have simply assumed that we have available a predictive contour, derived from the previous frame. Now 67 let us examine a method for producing such a prediction. Since we have several constraints to maintain the shape of 69 the snake, we found that the precision of the predictive contour could be relaxed. In this paper, we use a fast contour 71 matching method based on ICM [CITATION_1] .",
